# Matrix Builds

##    Jenkins Pipeline - Matrix Build
you will learn how to **run the same build on multiple envirnments**.

pipeline {
    agent any
    environment {
        INSTITUTE_NAME = "Pathnex"
    }
    matrix {
        axes {
            axis {
                name 'JAVA_VERSION'
                value '8, '11, ;17'
            }
        }
        stages {
            stage('Build')
                steps {
                    sh "echo Building with Java $JAVA_VERSION"
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

##    GitLab CI - Matrix Jobs
you will learn how to **run Jobs across multiple enviuronmnts using matrix**.

stages:
  - build

bulls:
  stage: build
  iamge: mavem:3.8.1-jdk-17
  parallel:
    matrix:
      - JAVA_VERSION: ['8', '11', '17']
  script:
    - echo "Building with Java $JAVA_VERSION"
